messages.messageBody:
I am so glad I found this group. I'm learning new things with every
message. When I was in Army ROTC at St. John's University, I studied
japanese military history and it was a godsend. Something about it
seemed much more appealing than other military campaigns, I dont know
what. Thanks for letting me join this group

Gabriel
